5:19:26.000Z","msg":"最可惜係明明有個可以幫你嘅人俾班under 你老豆但又話會幫你嘅人趕走"},{"pid":"3ecdcc7514feca9f03ab9dbcecb22bcf1ad771f5","tid":500552,"uid":4105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:20:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我20年前比個男人綁架<br />\n晚晚比佢強奸中出<br />\n我03年反抗過一次<br />\n07年佢話強奸到17年就會放我走<br />\n點知後來佢反悔<br />\n我14年又反抗過一次 失敗左比佢打到豬頭咁樣<br />\n我決定放棄啦 隨便中出我啦 有飯比我食就得啦<br />\n尋日又比佢中出左但已經無曬感覺<br />\n#metoo</blockquote><br />\n最大鑊係個男人話佢自己係你老豆<br />\n但明明你唔識佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你老過你老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df38ae280ca48eb0347e928b4a8db3bb2733d0af","tid":500552,"uid":28163,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:23:58.000Z","msg":"比共產黨強姦左幾十年<br />\n又唔講"},{"pid":"8c1a02d3c81aa0847595e722aadf8af52756dea1","tid":500552,"uid":145126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:42:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>On9港豬以為打完篇飛機文就做左野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續比人強姦啦</blockquote><br />\n你都有份俾人姦㗎<br />\n你又做過啲乜？"},{"pid":"4b9ee17264f9a1cfc13021ee49c0ccc9978c73a1","tid":500552,"uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:11:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>報警囉 係度鳩up有撚用咩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ddd58645a624684438f571e3622abde2b04097","tid":500552,"uid":51796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:12:13.000Z","msg":"駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n#metoo"},{"pid":"9e39671de40ba084a6f3ae46c013155571bfd6ce","tid":500552,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:16:05.000Z","msg":"琴日行街見到過萬條女被異性強行拖手<br />\n應該個個都被強姦多過一次慘絕人寰"},{"pid":"a9efa5da8f7fa84bad451bf556c8fa74c69f5f19","tid":500552,"uid":61611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:17:16.000Z","msg":"#metoo"},{"pid":"88985cd40f089a675f29fcfb585b986b1b2146cb","tid":500552,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:43:52.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n好撚sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88814b60a7285d7d1b3b57560410da15c675c704","tid":500552,"uid":41292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T07:06:46.000Z","msg":"#metoo"},{"pid":"1e3ac064e17aa53c7f9a26485f038e9fb1e806d0","tid":500552,"uid":34410,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T07:14:26.000Z","msg":"好多人俾人強姦完之後有斯德哥爾摩症候群<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以為個強姦犯對自己好好 當係一家人"},{"pid":"175168d5e031a4282a9f3566cf11b1e0c86bdf4f","tid":500552,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T07:20:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>🐷原來有傻尻係睇唔明？</blockquote><br />\n大量港豬供應"},{"pid":"0300b922d3fddf4ea9eb9f50e31cd11524d55270","tid":500552,"uid":28524,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T07:24:56.000Z","msg":"初初見你俾人姦都好嬲，但成班仆街人人指鹿為馬，D街坊仲大叫「姦佢姦佢！」，到而家班街坊直頭一齊姦，我已經完全冇曬感覺，好撚無能為力，一個打唔低一萬個，你安心上路俾人繼續姦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc3da18081e6ee5fd7351fd446f8449677091f4","tid":500552,"uid":120892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T07:29:15.000Z","msg":"最慘係，無論打風落雨都要出去賺錢<br />\n然後今年佢慶祝強姦你20週年攞曬你d錢去洗<br />\n叫雞都要俾錢啦，佢強姦完搶埋錢之後叫你收聲呢度唔輪到你講野"},{"pid":"7c87406c8a081709d8d7eb060fb9419e03e6f0af","tid":500552,"uid":76470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T07:34:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>訓你隔離床嗰個一早乖乖地享受，仲有糖食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你反抗做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲奶埋人地袋底泥添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fecec5c203db786e364a6d28fde3b3fbc4253112","tid":500552,"uid":61462,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T08:47:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>On9港豬以為打完篇飛機文就做左野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續比人強姦啦</blockquote><br />\n你都有份俾人姦㗎<br />\n你又做過啲乜？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n主要幫吓手㩒住其他人唔好反抗囉， <br />\n會幫手搽吓KY會易入啲，<br />\n又有時幫手較正碌賓周嘅角度，<br />\n等呀爹哋姦得疏乎啲，<br />\n<br />\n啲新女好閪煩架， 係咁杻個屎忽，<br />\n係咁叫唔好入呀唔比入呀麻閪煩，<br />\n通常一巴煎埋去成個人就呆晒唔識還拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算再唔聽話，只要爹哋一開聲就即刻震晒自動擘髀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲女都知爹哋響你面前就笑騎騎....<br />\n<br />\n我一邊吹鳩硬呀爹哋<br />\n另一邊係咁上KY落條女個西，<br />\n再一手渣住爹哋條陰莖引落條女個閪，<br />\n再一野推條女埋去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得咗<br />\n<br />\n成個過程爹哋郁都唔使郁，<br />\n其實係爹哋自己唔鍾意郁，<br />\n佢話鍾意啲女自己主動，<br />\n唔好搞到好似強<del>姦</del>逼咁喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實有撚分別咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一路吉啲眼淚一路必出黎，<br />\n係啦係啦知你有矜持啦呀閨女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢啲野我哋個個之前都經歷過架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n第時慣咗就慢慢開始enjoy架啦....我估<br />\n<br />\n爹哋射嘅量好多，次次都滿出黎，<br />\n(不過聽講佢不育無咩精蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n我哋就講吓好多呀好傑呀好幸福呀爹哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通常呢個時候爹哋會讚吓我哋乖呀好聽話之類嘅廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後循例幫佢舐幾野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ， 再指揮其他人舐乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ,<br />\n<br />\n有時會有啲女想上位係咁追住爹哋個屎眼黎舐， <br />\n爹哋緊係知佢諗咩啦， 我作狀個嬲樣，<br />\n爹哋即係趁佢鑽到最入最忘我嗰時放講屁比佢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為我做得野又氹都爹哋鬼咁開心，我話悶唔開心佢比我隨時出去散心，<br />\n有機會逃走但係係呢樹有特權搵到食又舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出面風大雨大呀，就算同啲女我都係咁講架啦， 比啲藉口佢哋就唔願走咁啦，<br />\n<del>姦</del>做愛啫， 少忽肉咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又氹咗爹哋比咗好多錢我 <br />\n我靜雞雞響外面置咗個家， 識咗個男人,<br />\n成個Benedict Cumberbatch咁隻眼又藍又綠又金毛成隻鬼咁但係佢話自己係Chinese喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 是但啦...<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 已經兩個月無黎m, 我鼓起勇氣同爹哋講係佢嘅骨肉，見佢笑得好開心，<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解見到佢笑騎騎個笑容好眼熟.... 有啲寒....<br />\n無事嘅， 佢話過我好乖好錫我架....."},{"pid":"2eda1c9c997f9eff65eb021f18ad2bfe5188a7e0","tid":500552,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T08:48:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>d比喻真係好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70cd318a390f4bedebef7fc650f967b540dd9431","tid":500552,"uid":61462,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T09:09:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>d比喻真係好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n柒得過你哋咁鍾意舐屎眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e13ff4d46ba203f79c24abbf15115d5fdd83e850","tid":500552,"uid":59684,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T09:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"